'global' parameters:
For each of these last four parameters there is a similarly named 'global' parameter that can be used instead.
The 'global' version of the parameter will affect other New generation packages as well as New Donations.
Using the 'global' version ensures that all the New generation login panels have these four features set the same way.
Each New generation package will have its own set so that the parameters can also be set independently.

The 'global' versions use the prefix 'g2', i.e.
g2nouserpw
g2omitfields
g2mustfields
g2statesdd

